          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Let Seniors Work Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> Amends title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) of the Social Security Act to: (1) eliminate the payroll tax for individuals who have attained retirement age, and (2) remove the limitation on the amount of outside income which a beneficiary may earn (earnings test) without incurring a reduction in benefits.</p>]]></text>
